Annotation
URI of a policy/rule-combining algorithm to be added to supported algorithms. There must be one and only one Java class - say 'com.example.FooCombiningAlg' - on the classpath implementing interface 'org.ow2.authzforce.core.pdp.api.combining.CombiningAlg' with zero-arg constructor, such that this URI equals: new com.example.FooCombiningAlg().getId().
